Name: Strip 4: Classmate Study
About the game: A girl from school has invited you to study for exams. She is bored and asking you to play. Classic tabletop game in an intimate atmosphere. Connect four (aka Four in a row, Gravitrips) combined with strip game. Every time you win, she will take off one piece of clothes. All characters are over the age of 18.
